                    h1(class="px-4 py-3 w-5/6 text-center text-gray-600 font-bold") 구글 아이디로 로그인하기
                form(action="/api/login/loginSuccess", method="post") 
                    div(class="mt-4")
                        label(class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2") 아이디
                        input(name="id" , class="bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline border border-gray-300 rounded py-2 px-4 block w-full appearance-none")
                    div(class="mt-4")
                        div(class="flex justify-between")
                            label(class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2") 비밀번호
                            a(href="#" class="text-xs text-gray-500") 비밀번호 찾기
                        input(name="pw" ,class="bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline border border-gray-300 rounded py-2 px-4 block w-full appearance-none" type="password")
                    div(class="mt-8")
                        button(class="bg-gray-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 w-full rounded hover:bg-gray-600") 로그인
                div(class="mt-4 flex items-center justify-between")
                    span(class="border-b w-1/5 md:w-1/4")
                    a(href="/api/join" class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase") 회원가입
                    span(class="border-b w-1/5 md:w-1/4")
        footer(class="absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-white border-t border-gray-400 shadow")
            div(class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto flex py-8")
                div(class="w-full mx-auto flex")
                    div(class="flex w-full md:w-1/2 ")
                        div(class="px-8")
                            h3(class="font-bold text-gray-900") About
                            p(class="py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm")
                                Lorem 수로그에 오신것을 환영합니다...!
                    div(class="flex w-full md:w-1/2")
                        div(class="px-8")
                            h3(class="font-bold text-gray-900") Contact
                            ul(class="list-reset items-center text-sm pt-3")
                                li
                                    a(class="inline-block text-gray-600 no-underline hover:text-gray-900 hover:text-underline py-1" href="https://github.com/tnqls0624" target="_blank") git hub